Description: A Potion of Resilience can be used once to grant a player immunity from roleblocks for 2 nights
An Invisibility Cloak will keep your visits hidden from roles like the Stalker, Harlot or Insomniac
Manacles of Spite allow you to roleblock a player each night. If you do, you will also roleblock yourself.

A Fjät Rune allows you to stalk a player at night to find out who they visit. Holding it will make you appear as a Witch Craft user to intel checks. After use, a Rune must recharge and can be used again by you three nights later. If you pass the Rune to a different player they will be able to use it immediately.
A Potion of Acquiescence can be used once to steal any items the target player has
The Heart of Fenrir is a powerful wolf relic that grants night immunity to its bearer. If you are holding it and there are no other werewolves left alive, you will become an Omegawolf.
A Wolf Pelt will protect you from one night kill, but it will make you appear as a Werewolf to the Seer
If you are killed at night whilst in the possession of an Ankh of Reincarnation, you will be revived a day later
A Dreamcatcher will let you know who visited you in the night
A Disruption Orb will roleblock anyone visiting you that is not Night Immune. Unfortunately it will also roleblock you at the same time

A Hvísla Rune allows you to talk to a player the following night. The other player will see all the messages you send at night but will not know who is sending them. Holding it will make you appear as a Witch Craft user to intel checks. After use, a Rune must recharge and can be used again by you three nights later. If you pass the Rune to a different player they will be able to use it immediately.
A crossbow can kill a player at night. It can only be used once. Protection will stop the kill, and if the Huntsman catches you trying to kill someone they are guarding, you will both die.
The Ring of Tenacity prevents its bearer from being Roleblocked
A Potion of Clarity allows you to find out a player's role

A Hvísla Rune allows you to talk to a player the following night. The other player will see all the messages you send at night but will not know who is sending them. Holding it will make you appear as a Witch Craft user to intel checks. After use, a Rune must recharge and can be used again by you three nights later. If you pass the Rune to a different player they will be able to use it immediately.
A Potion of Vulnerability will remove any night immunity from a player the night after it is used
A Potion of Pollymorph allows you to turn a player into a parrot for the duration of a day
The Accurrum can be used once per game. The day after it is activated will be shorter than normal
